imdb.title: God, I'm Not Ready
synopsis: The lives of four people from different walks of life who hear the call into ministry and the trials and tribulations they face when answering the call. The chosen five have told God they are not ready, some continue in their sins while the others battle the fight in faith against their sins and past lives. God see's their hearts and allows them to make their own choices.Jesus, Angel Michael, Angel Gabriel are among those on earth living among them ready to help them with making the right choice for their life and lifestyle. While Lucifer and his messengers come to give opposition plus stir up trouble. God's places his messengers strategically in aiding the humans onto the right path, while Lucifer has his own messengers in place to cause havoc. Walking along with the humans, blending with the community. Jesus and Lucifer both are out to gain powerThe four individuals must all take a final stance and answer God or their fate will be made for them. Lucifer calls Jesus out to battle once and for all for the lives of the chosen four. When Jesus and his Arch Angels embrace the chosen for by allowing them to make their own decisions. Leaving the past behind or allowing their past lives to control them. The future is bright for a few yet for the others they must come to terms with their forgiveness or bitterness. This battle is not in the spirit yet a natural battle here on earth with the chosen five. Who will they stand with? Who will they turn to?
